<plot>Carla Marins is a novice nun who carries the map for a hidden bag of diamonds tattooed in her own body. When a whole family of criminals find out, they start chasing her and make her take the habit off (in every way) all to get the 'map', even by seduction... or force. But one of the persecutors suddenly falls in love with her.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?404635</url></doc>
